# ROVEXO v1.0 — No Manual Override Contract

**STATUS: APPROVED | PROTECTED | PERMANENT**

No role or system may override deployment, certification, protected contracts,
migration, database, Full Demo, Homepage freeze, or Final Release Protection.

Forbidden for Super Admin, Product Owner, Staff, Developers, Deployment Center,
Vercel, CI/CD, and Release Actions:

- Deploy anyway / force deploy
- Skip tests / skip gates / skip certification
- Ignore failures / disable gates / disable certification
- Override failures / bypass contracts

Scores of 97%, 98%, 99%, or 99.999% are blocked. Only exactly 100% PASS with
certification, protection, no blockers, and no failures allows live deployment.

Never accept override payload keys or env flags. Never weaken this rule.
